- Hopcroft, J. "An n log n Algorithm for Minimizing States in a Finite Automaton" (1971)
- Brzozowski, J. "Canonical Regular Expressions and Minimal State Graphs" (1962)
- Watson, B. "A Taxonomy of Finite Automata Minimization Algorithms" (1993)
